name: Crown Wood Eyewear
tag_list: eco, sunglasses, accessories, bamboo, polarized, fashion, design, startups
overview: Crown Wood Eyewear is a premium sunglass company that offers unique style with a classic look. Crown Wood Eyewear’s exclusivity is what makes them so unique. They offer 3 styles of sunglasses; Premium all Italian Acetate sunglasses, Mixed Italian acetate and Eco friendly Chinese bamboo sunglasses, and all Eco friendly Chinese bamboo sunglasses. The lenses are polarized 4x and scratch/impact resistant approved by the FDA. Crown Wood Eyewear features Swiss steel spring hinges as well as 5 barrel hinges, all top of the line materials. Not only are these sunglasses extremely high quality, they are also affordable. Crown Wood Eyewear offers designer quality sunglasses without the designer price tag.
